<p class="courseblockdesc">
Placement in a forensic science or toxicology laboratory or setting, under the supervision of a faculty member, with an accepted research project or paper required. Course Information: May be repeated to a maximum of 4 hours. Students may register in more than one section per term. Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=BPS%20580" title="BPS&#160;580" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'BPS 580');">BPS&#160;580</a>; and consent of the instructor and a minimum of 15 hours of credit earned in the M.S. in Forensic Science program.<br />
