<p class="courseblockdesc">
Supervised research in forensic science; a research project to be designed and completed within one semester. Course Information: Satisfactory/Unsatisfactory grading only. Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=BPS%20580" title="BPS&#160;580" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'BPS 580');">BPS&#160;580</a>; and at least the core course in the M.S. in Forensic Science program covering the subject area in which the research is to be conducted and consent of the instructor.<br />
