</div><div class="courseblock">
<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>BPS&#160;599.  Dissertation Research.  0-16 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Ph.D. thesis research. Course Information: Satisfactory/Unsatisfactory grading only. May be repeated. Prerequisite(s): Consent of the instructor.<br />
</p>
